    "dsl_program": "[CODE]show sqrt(16 9)\n[EXCEPTION]invalid syntax. Perhaps you forgot a comma?\n[COMMENT]Separate function arguments with commas.\n[CODE]show sqrt(16)\n[RESULT]4.0\nThe square root is $RESULT.",
    "output_json": {
      "__STATEMENT__": "The square root is 4.0."
    }
  },

  // SYN-09: 括弧の不整合（Mismatched Parentheses）の修復
  {
    "instruction": "Calculate the cosine of zero. The closing parenthesis is missing. Detect the syntax error, repair it, and continue.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]show cos(0\n[EXCEPTION]'(' was never closed.\n[COMMENT]Close the parenthesis before evaluating the expression.\n[CODE]show cos(0)\n[RESULT]1.0\n[CODE]$value = float $RESULT\nThe cosine value is $value.",
    "output_json": {
      "value": 1.0,
      "__STATEMENT__": "The cosine value is 1.0."
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "Access a list element using a computed index. The parenthesis in the index expression is not closed. Repair the syntax error and continue.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]$numbers = list 10, 20, 30\n[CODE]show $numbers.(1 + 1\n[EXCEPTION]'(' was never closed.\n[COMMENT]The computed index expression must have matching parentheses.\n[CODE]show $numbers.(1 + 1)\n[RESULT]30\nThe selected number is $RESULT.",
    "output_json": {
      "numbers": [
        10,
        20,
        30
      ],
      "__STATEMENT__": "The selected number is 30."
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "複雑な数式を書いている途中で括弧を閉じ忘れました。構文エラーを修正してください。",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]show (3 + 5 * (2 + 1)\n[EXCEPTION]'(' was never closed.\n[COMMENT]Every opening parenthesis must have a matching closing parenthesis.\n[CODE]show (3 + 5 * (2 + 1))\n[RESULT]18\nThe calculated value is $RESULT.",
    "output_json": {
      "__STATEMENT__": "The calculated value is 18."
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "Create a nested list. One closing parenthesis is missing from the definition. Detect the syntax error, repair it, and continue.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]show list(list 1, 2\n[EXCEPTION]'(' was never closed.\n[COMMENT]Complete the nested expression by closing the parenthesis.\n[CODE]show list(list 1, 2)\n[RESULT][[1, 2]]\nNested list created successfully.",
    "output_json": {
      "__STATEMENT__": "Nested list created successfully."
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "Output a sentence containing escaped parentheses. The program mistakenly leaves a real parenthesis unclosed. Detect the syntax error, repair it, and continue.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]show (\"ball\\(s\\)\"\n[EXCEPTION]'(' was never closed.\n[COMMENT]The escaped parentheses inside the string are correct. Only the outer expression needs a closing parenthesis.\n[CODE]show (\"ball\\(s\\)\")\n[RESULT]ball\\(s\\)\nThe word is $RESULT.",
    "output_json": {
      "__STATEMENT__": "The word is ball\\(s\\)."
    }
  },

