  // 5. エラー系（物理）：12シチュエーション (PHYS-01 〜 PHYS-12)

  // PHYS-01: ロボットのつまずき（Stumbled）と歩行リカバリ
  {
    "instruction": "A humanoid robot stumbled while walking over loose gravel. Use the following libraries.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data to tensor.\n\nimport humanoid_a\n  - capture_posture() -> tensor : Acquire current body posture.\n  - walk_forward(distance: float) -> None : Walk forward.\n  - estimate_instability() -> str : Estimate the dominant instability.\n  - recover_balance(mode: str) -> None : Execute a balance recovery behavior.\n  - resume_walk() -> None : Resume walking after recovery.\n\nIf a recoverable physical error occurs, analyze the situation and recover safely.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import humanoid_a\n[CODE]$pose = tensor capture_posture()\n[CODE]walk_forward(4.0)\n[EXCEPTION]BalanceException: Foot slipped on loose gravel.\n[COMMENT]Select an appropriate recovery according to the instability estimate.\n[CODE]show estimate_instability()\n[RESULT]\"forward\"\n[CODE]recover_balance(\"forward\")\n[CODE]resume_walk()",
    "output_json": {
      "pose": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": "",
      "recovery_mode": "forward"
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "A warehouse transport robot lost balance while climbing a loading ramp.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data to tensor.\n\nimport warehouse_bot\n  - read_motion_state() -> tensor : Read motion state.\n  - climb_ramp() -> None : Climb the ramp.\n  - classify_fault() -> str : Classify the detected physical fault.\n  - stabilize_chassis(profile: str) -> tensor : Recover chassis stability.\n  - adapt_policy(loss: tensor) -> None : Update recovery policy.\n\nIf recovery succeeds, continue operation.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import warehouse_bot\n[CODE]$state = tensor read_motion_state()\n[CODE]climb_ramp()\n[EXCEPTION]BalanceException: Rear wheel lost traction during ascent.\n[COMMENT]Choose the stabilization profile before adaptation.\n[CODE]show classify_fault()\n[RESULT]\"rear_slip\"\n[CODE]$loss = tensor stabilize_chassis(\"rear_slip\")\n[CODE]adapt_policy($loss)",
    "output_json": {
      "state": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "loss": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": ""
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "歩行中のサービスロボットがカーペットの端に足を引っ掛けました。\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: テンソルへ変換します。\n\nimport service_robot\n  - sense_gait() -> tensor : 歩容状態を取得\n  - patrol() -> None : 巡回歩行\n  - diagnose_step() -> str : 異常な足運びを診断\n  - perform_side_step(direction: str) -> None : 横ステップで回復\n  - continue_patrol() -> None : 巡回を再開\n\n異常を分析し、安全に回復してください。",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import service_robot\n[CODE]$gait = tensor sense_gait()\n[CODE]patrol()\n[EXCEPTION]BalanceException: Foot caught on carpet edge.\n[COMMENT]Use a lateral recovery step when appropriate.\n[CODE]show diagnose_step()\n[RESULT]\"left\"\n[CODE]perform_side_step(\"left\")\n[CODE]continue_patrol()",
    "output_json": {
      "gait": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": "",
      "direction": "left"
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "A delivery robot carrying a package leaned forward after hitting a floor gap.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data to tensor.\n\nimport courier_bot\n  - payload_state() -> tensor : Read payload dynamics.\n  - deliver_package() -> None : Continue delivery.\n  - analyze_payload_shift() -> str : Analyze load movement.\n  - compensate_center_of_mass(mode: str) -> tensor : Recover balance.\n  - update_controller(loss: tensor) -> None : Improve the controller.\n\nRecover while protecting the payload.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import courier_bot\n[CODE]$payload = tensor payload_state()\n[CODE]deliver_package()\n[EXCEPTION]PayloadException: Forward load shift detected.\n[COMMENT]Select the center-of-mass compensation strategy.\n[CODE]show analyze_payload_shift()\n[RESULT]\"front_heavy\"\n[CODE]$loss = tensor compensate_center_of_mass(\"front_heavy\")\n[CODE]update_controller($loss)",
    "output_json": {
      "payload": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "loss": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": ""
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "A night patrol robot encountered an unexpected curb in a dark environment.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data to tensor.\n\nimport patrol_unit\n  - observe_motion() -> tensor : Observe current motion.\n  - advance() -> None : Move forward.\n  - inspect_incident() -> str : Inspect the cause of instability.\n  - execute_safe_stop() -> None : Stop safely.\n  - regain_posture() -> None : Restore a stable standing posture.\n  - continue_route() -> None : Resume the patrol route.\n\nRecover safely without unnecessary learning updates.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import patrol_unit\n[CODE]$motion = tensor observe_motion()\n[CODE]advance()\n[EXCEPTION]NavigationException: Unexpected curb contact detected.\n[COMMENT]Perform a conservative recovery when visibility is limited.\n[CODE]show inspect_incident()\n[RESULT]\"low_visibility\"\n[CODE]execute_safe_stop()\n[CODE]regain_posture()\n[CODE]continue_route()",
    "output_json": {
      "motion": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": "",
      "incident": "low_visibility"
    }
  },

  // PHYS-02: 物体の把持失敗（Grasp Failed）と再アプローチ
  {
    "instruction": "A robotic manipulator failed to grasp a slippery plastic bottle.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport manipulator_x\n  - capture_grasp_state() -> tensor : Acquire the current grasp state.\n  - grasp_object() -> None : Attempt to grasp the target.\n  - inspect_contact() -> str : Analyze the cause of the failed grasp.\n  - retry_grasp(mode: str) -> None : Retry using an alternative grasp strategy.\n  - continue_task() -> None : Resume the interrupted task.\n\nIf grasping fails, analyze the failure and recover safely.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import manipulator_x\n[CODE]$grasp = tensor capture_grasp_state()\n[CODE]grasp_object()\n[EXCEPTION]GraspException: Object slipped during contact.\n[COMMENT]Select a grasp strategy appropriate for the detected contact condition.\n[CODE]show inspect_contact()\n[RESULT]\"low_friction\"\n[CODE]retry_grasp(\"low_friction\")\n[CODE]continue_task()",
    "output_json": {
      "grasp": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": "",
      "contact": "low_friction"
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "A laboratory robot deformed a paper cup while attempting to pick it up.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport lab_assistant\n  - read_gripper_state() -> tensor : Read the current gripper state.\n  - pick_sample() -> None : Pick up the sample.\n  - estimate_material() -> str : Estimate the material response.\n  - adjust_grip(profile: str) -> tensor : Execute an adaptive grasp.\n  - refine_gripper(loss: tensor) -> None : Update the grasp controller.\n\nRecover the grasp while minimizing deformation.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import lab_assistant\n[CODE]$gripper = tensor read_gripper_state()\n[CODE]pick_sample()\n[EXCEPTION]ManipulatorException: Excessive deformation detected.\n[COMMENT]Choose a compliant gripping profile before adaptation.\n[CODE]show estimate_material()\n[RESULT]\"soft_surface\"\n[CODE]$loss = tensor adjust_grip(\"soft_surface\")\n[CODE]refine_gripper($loss)",
    "output_json": {
      "gripper": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "loss": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": ""
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "棚の商品を把持しようとしたところ、位置ずれにより空振りしました。\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: テンソルへ変換します。\n\nimport shelf_picker\n  - scan_workspace() -> tensor : 作業空間を取得\n  - pick_item() -> None : 商品を把持\n  - evaluate_alignment() -> str : 位置ずれを評価\n  - rescan_target() -> None : 対象を再スキャン\n  - retry_pick(offset: str) -> None : 補正後に再把持\n\n把持失敗時は原因を分析して適切に回復してください。",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import shelf_picker\n[CODE]$scene = tensor scan_workspace()\n[CODE]pick_item()\n[EXCEPTION]ManipulatorException: Target position mismatch detected.\n[COMMENT]Perform a new scan before retrying the grasp.\n[CODE]show evaluate_alignment()\n[RESULT]\"right_offset\"\n[CODE]rescan_target()\n[CODE]retry_pick(\"right_offset\")",
    "output_json": {
      "scene": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": "",
      "offset": "right_offset"
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "An industrial robot failed to hold a heavy metal component because of gradual slipping.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport assembly_arm\n  - monitor_grasp() -> tensor : Monitor grasp quality.\n  - lift_component() -> None : Lift the workpiece.\n  - measure_slip() -> str : Measure the slipping condition.\n  - increase_holding_force(level: str) -> tensor : Apply a stronger holding strategy.\n  - update_estimator(loss: tensor) -> None : Improve the slip estimator.\n\nRecover without dropping the component.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import assembly_arm\n[CODE]$monitor = tensor monitor_grasp()\n[CODE]lift_component()\n[EXCEPTION]GraspException: Progressive slipping detected.\n[COMMENT]Increase holding force according to the measured slip level.\n[CODE]show measure_slip()\n[RESULT]\"moderate\"\n[CODE]$loss = tensor increase_holding_force(\"moderate\")\n[CODE]update_estimator($loss)",
    "output_json": {
