      "loss": {
	"__type__": "tensor",
	"__value__": null
      },
      "__STATEMENT__": ""
    }
  },
  {
    "instruction": "A domestic robot attempted to pick up a soft stuffed toy, but the object compressed excessively.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport home_helper\n  - observe_gripper() -> tensor : Observe the gripper state.\n  - pick_up() -> None : Pick up the object.\n  - identify_object_response() -> str : Analyze deformation characteristics.\n  - enable_soft_grasp(mode: str) -> None : Switch to a compliant grasp mode.\n  - resume_cleanup() -> None : Resume the cleaning task.\n\nRecover using a grasp strategy suitable for deformable objects.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import home_helper\n[CODE]$state = tensor observe_gripper()\n[CODE]pick_up()\n[EXCEPTION]ManipulatorException: Excessive object deformation detected.\n[COMMENT]Select a compliant grasp mode for deformable objects.\n[CODE]show identify_object_response()\n[RESULT]\"compressible\"\n[CODE]enable_soft_grasp(\"compressible\")\n[CODE]resume_cleanup()",
    "output_json": {
