  // PHYS-03: 介護ロボットの「持ち上げ」時のバランス不整合
  {
    "instruction": "A nursing assistant robot became unstable while lifting a patient from a bed.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport care_lifter\n  - capture_support_state() -> tensor : Capture the current support posture.\n  - lift_patient() -> None : Begin the lifting motion.\n  - evaluate_stability() -> str : Analyze the primary cause of instability.\n  - engage_leg_support(mode: str) -> tensor : Activate lower-body stabilization.\n  - optimize_posture(loss: tensor) -> None : Improve future lifting behavior.\n\nIf instability occurs, recover safely while protecting the patient.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import care_lifter\n[CODE]$support = tensor capture_support_state()\n[CODE]lift_patient()\n[EXCEPTION]BalanceException: Patient shifted unexpectedly during lifting.\n[COMMENT]Select a stabilization strategy based on the patient's movement.\n[CODE]show evaluate_stability()\n[RESULT]\"forward_shift\"\n[CODE]$loss = tensor engage_leg_support(\"forward_shift\")\n[CODE]optimize_posture($loss)",
