  {
    "instruction": "An underwater inspection robot detected abnormal battery temperature during a long mission.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport subsea_probe\n  - inspect_power_module() -> tensor : Inspect the battery module.\n  - survey_pipeline() -> None : Survey an underwater pipeline.\n  - estimate_temperature_risk() -> bool : Determine whether overheating is likely.\n  - disable_high_power_tools() -> None : Disable nonessential equipment.\n  - ascend_to_surface() -> None : Return safely to the surface.\n\nReduce thermal stress before continuing any mission activity.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import subsea_probe\n[CODE]$module = tensor inspect_power_module()\n[CODE]survey_pipeline()\n[EXCEPTION]BatteryException: Battery temperature continued to rise despite normal workload.\n[COMMENT]Lower power consumption before the battery reaches its protection limit.\n[CODE]show estimate_temperature_risk()\n[RESULT]true\n[CODE]disable_high_power_tools()\n[CODE]ascend_to_surface()",
