    "instruction": "An agricultural drone exhausted its battery reserve before reaching either the charging station or its home position.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport crop_drone\n  - inspect_flight_state() -> tensor : Observe the flight state.\n  - spray_field() -> None : Perform crop spraying.\n  - evaluate_emergency_landing() -> bool : Determine whether an emergency landing is required.\n  - land_immediately() -> None : Perform an emergency landing.\n  - transmit_location() -> None : Report the landing position.\n\nIf no safe return is possible, terminate the mission safely.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import crop_drone\n[CODE]$flight = tensor inspect_flight_state()\n[CODE]spray_field()\n[EXCEPTION]BatteryException: Remaining energy is insufficient to reach a recovery point.\n[COMMENT]Protect the vehicle by performing a controlled landing before total power loss.\n[CODE]show evaluate_emergency_landing()\n[RESULT]true\n[CODE]land_immediately()\n[CODE]transmit_location()\n[CODE]raise BatteryException: \"Mission terminated after emergency landing.\"",
