  {
    "instruction": "An autonomous forklift detected an unstable pallet while lifting it.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport forklift_auto\n  - forklift_auto_inspect_payload() -> tensor : Observe the payload.\n  - forklift_auto_lift_pallet() -> None : Lift the pallet.\n  - forklift_auto_analyze_load_balance() -> dict : Analyze load balance.\n  - forklift_auto_lower_forks() -> None : Lower the forks.\n  - forklift_auto_reposition_pallet(offset: float) -> None : Correct the pallet position.\n  - forklift_auto_resume_lifting() -> None : Resume lifting.\n\nRecover by stabilizing the payload before continuing.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import forklift_auto\n[CODE]$payload = tensor forklift_auto_inspect_payload()\n[CODE]forklift_auto_lift_pallet()\n[EXCEPTION]PayloadException: The load shifted beyond the stable lifting envelope.\n[COMMENT]An unstable load should be repositioned before any additional lifting.\n[CODE]show forklift_auto_analyze_load_balance()\n[RESULT]{\"offset\":0.12,\"stable\":false}\n[CODE]$balance = dict $RESULT\n[CODE]forklift_auto_lower_forks()\n[CODE]forklift_auto_reposition_pallet($balance.offset)\n[CODE]forklift_auto_resume_lifting()",
