  {
    "instruction": "A drone encountered strong crosswinds while flying through a mountain valley.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport valley_drone\n  - observe_flight_state() -> tensor : Observe the current flight state.\n  - inspect_route() -> None : Continue the planned route.\n  - reconstruct_airflow() -> tensor : Estimate the surrounding airflow.\n  - predict_safe_corridor(flow: tensor) -> tensor : Predict a safer flight corridor.\n  - redirect_flight(path: tensor) -> None : Follow the new flight path.\n  - cache_wind_model(flow: tensor) -> None : Cache the airflow estimate for future flights.\n\nRecover while minimizing unnecessary control oscillation.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import valley_drone\n[CODE]$flight = tensor observe_flight_state()\n[CODE]inspect_route()\n[EXCEPTION]FlightException: Crosswind gusts repeatedly pushed the aircraft away from its planned trajectory.\n[COMMENT]A stable detour is preferable to aggressive attitude corrections.\n[CODE]$flow = tensor reconstruct_airflow()\n[CODE]$path = tensor predict_safe_corridor($flow)\n[CODE]redirect_flight($path)\n[CODE]cache_wind_model($flow)",
