    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import rescue_unit\n[CODE]$environment = tensor sample_environment()\n[CODE]search_survivors()\n[EXCEPTION]SensorException: Dense smoke significantly reduced ranging reliability.\n[COMMENT]Reliable perception is more valuable than rapid exploration in hazardous environments.\n[CODE]$fusion = tensor fuse_sensor_data()\n[CODE]show evaluate_confidence($fusion)\n[RESULT]0.57\n[CODE]enable_cautious_mode()\n[CODE]synchronize_map($fusion)",
