  {
    "instruction": "An autonomous harvesting robot found that ripe fruit was heavily occluded by branches.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport orchard_picker\n  - acquire_depth_map() -> tensor : Acquire a depth map.\n  - harvest() -> None : Harvest the target crop.\n  - reconstruct_canopy(depth: tensor) -> tensor : Reconstruct the surrounding branches.\n  - rank_grasp_candidates(model: tensor) -> list : Rank candidate grasp paths.\n  - execute_candidate(order: list) -> bool : Execute the preferred candidate.\n  - archive_failure_case() -> None : Record difficult harvesting situations.\n\nRecover by choosing a safer harvesting path instead of forcing access.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import orchard_picker\n[CODE]$depth = tensor acquire_depth_map()\n[CODE]harvest()\n[EXCEPTION]OcclusionException: Branches completely blocked the planned picking path.\n[COMMENT]Damaging the crop is worse than delaying a single harvest attempt.\n[CODE]$model = tensor reconstruct_canopy($depth)\n[CODE]show rank_grasp_candidates($model)\n[RESULT][\"upper_arc\",\"left_entry\",\"retry_later\"]\n[CODE]$order = list $RESULT\n[CODE]execute_candidate($order)\n[CODE]archive_failure_case()",
