  // PHYS-10: ロボットハンドの滑り落ち（Object Slipping）
  {
    "instruction": "An autonomous mining robot detected excessive vibration from its drilling mechanism.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport mining_robot\n  - monitor_drill() -> tensor : Observe drill dynamics.\n  - drill_rock() -> None : Perform drilling.\n  - estimate_resonance() -> tensor : Estimate the resonance characteristics.\n  - retune_controller(model: tensor) -> None : Adjust the drilling controller.\n  - verify_stability() -> bool : Verify that vibration has stabilized.\n  - resume_drilling() -> None : Resume drilling.\n\nAvoid operating near resonant frequencies whenever possible.",
