  {
    "instruction": "倉庫ロボットが通路の床面に大きな段差を検知しました。\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: テンソルへ変換します。\n\nimport logistics_runner\n  - capture_depth_map() -> tensor : 深度マップを取得\n  - deliver_container() -> None : コンテナを搬送\n  - reconstruct_surface(depth: tensor) -> tensor : 路面形状を復元\n  - score_routes(surface: tensor) -> list : 通行候補を評価\n  - switch_route(candidates: list) -> None : 経路を変更\n  - update_navigation_cache(surface: tensor) -> None : 地形情報を保存\n\n危険な段差を越えるより安全な迂回を優先してください。",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import logistics_runner\n[CODE]$depth = tensor capture_depth_map()\n[CODE]deliver_container()\n[EXCEPTION]NavigationException: A floor height change exceeded the vehicle's clearance.\n[COMMENT]Prefer a predictable detour instead of challenging uncertain terrain.\n[CODE]$surface = tensor reconstruct_surface($depth)\n[CODE]show score_routes($surface)\n[RESULT][\"north_corridor\",\"service_lane\"]\n[CODE]$routes = list $RESULT\n[CODE]switch_route($routes)\n[CODE]update_navigation_cache($surface)",
