    "instruction": "An aerial inspection drone temporarily lost GNSS reception while flying between high-rise buildings.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport city_drone\n  - inspect_navigation() -> tensor : Observe navigation status.\n  - inspect_bridge() -> None : Inspect the assigned bridge.\n  - estimate_localization() -> dict : Evaluate localization reliability.\n  - enable_visual_odometry() -> None : Switch to visual odometry.\n  - synchronize_local_map() -> None : Synchronize the local map.\n\nContinue only if localization remains sufficiently reliable.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import city_drone\n[CODE]$navigation = tensor inspect_navigation()\n[CODE]inspect_bridge()\n[EXCEPTION]LocalizationException: Satellite positioning became unavailable inside the urban canyon.\n[COMMENT]Maintaining reliable localization is more important than following the original flight schedule.\n[CODE]show estimate_localization()\n[RESULT]{\"confidence\":0.91,\"visual_odometry\":true}\n[CODE]$status = dict $RESULT\n[CODE]enable_visual_odometry()\n[CODE]synchronize_local_map()",
