  {
    "instruction": "An autonomous firefighting robot detected structural collapse risk while operating inside a damaged building.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport fire_response\n  - observe_structure() -> tensor : Observe the surrounding structure.\n  - extinguish_fire() -> None : Perform firefighting.\n  - predict_collapse() -> dict : Predict structural stability.\n  - withdraw(distance: float) -> None : Move to a safer position.\n  - transmit_hazard_report(report: dict) -> None : Report the detected hazard.\n\nIf the environment is no longer safe for autonomous operation, terminate the mission.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import fire_response\n[CODE]$structure = tensor observe_structure()\n[CODE]extinguish_fire()\n[EXCEPTION]HazardException: Structural deformation accelerated beyond the safety threshold.\n[COMMENT]Protecting the robot preserves future rescue capability.\n[CODE]show predict_collapse()\n[RESULT]{\"evacuate\":true,\"distance\":12.0}\n[CODE]$hazard = dict $RESULT\n[CODE]withdraw($hazard.distance)\n[CODE]transmit_hazard_report($hazard)\n[CODE]raise HazardException: \"Autonomous firefighting suspended due to collapse risk.\"",
