  {
    "instruction": "物流ロボットがエレベーターの到着予定時刻を大幅に超えて待機しています。\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: テンソルへ変換します。\n\nimport logistics_helper\n  - observe_schedule() -> tensor : スケジュール状態を取得\n  - transport_item() -> None : 荷物を搬送\n  - predict_delay() -> dict : 待ち時間を予測\n  - evaluate_alternative_routes(report: dict) -> list : 代替経路を評価\n  - follow_route(route: str) -> None : 新しい経路へ移動\n  - remember_delay(report: dict) -> None : 遅延情報を記録\n\n待機時間が長い場合は別経路を優先してください。",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import logistics_helper\n[CODE]$schedule = tensor observe_schedule()\n[CODE]transport_item()\n[EXCEPTION]SchedulingException: Elevator service was delayed beyond the expected operating window.\n[COMMENT]Long waits reduce fleet efficiency more than taking a modest detour.\n[CODE]show predict_delay()\n[RESULT]{\"minutes\":8,\"reason\":\"maintenance\"}\n[CODE]$delay = dict $RESULT\n[CODE]show evaluate_alternative_routes($delay)\n[RESULT][\"west_ramp\",\"north_lift\"]\n[CODE]$routes = list $RESULT\n[CODE]follow_route(\"west_ramp\")\n[CODE]remember_delay($delay)",
