    "instruction": "An agricultural robot detected inconsistent localization after crossing a narrow bridge between fields.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport field_navigator\n  - inspect_pose() -> tensor : Observe the current pose estimate.\n  - navigate_field() -> None : Navigate through the field.\n  - fuse_localization() -> tensor : Fuse multiple localization sources.\n  - compute_pose_covariance(model: tensor) -> tensor : Estimate localization uncertainty.\n  - recalibrate_localization(stats: tensor) -> None : Recalibrate localization.\n  - persist_calibration() -> None : Save calibration data.\n\nReduce localization uncertainty before continuing autonomous travel.",
    "dsl_program": "[CODE]import tensor\n[CODE]import field_navigator\n[CODE]$pose = tensor inspect_pose()\n[CODE]navigate_field()\n[EXCEPTION]LocalizationException: Position estimates diverged after crossing uneven terrain.\n[COMMENT]Reliable localization is essential before autonomous navigation resumes.\n[CODE]$fusion = tensor fuse_localization()\n[CODE]$covariance = tensor compute_pose_covariance($fusion)\n[CODE]recalibrate_localization($covariance)\n[CODE]persist_calibration()",
