  {
    "instruction": "A multi-robot construction team detected that a bridge inspection robot had become immobilized on a temporary platform.\n\nimport tensor\n  - tensor <expr>: convert data into a tensor.\n\nimport bridge_team\n  - bridge_team_inspect_team_state() -> tensor : Observe the current team state.\n  - bridge_team_inspect_bridge() -> None : Continue the inspection mission.\n  - bridge_team_secure_worksite() -> None : Prevent nearby robots from entering the hazardous area.\n  - bridge_team_reconstruct_scene() -> tensor : Reconstruct the surrounding environment.\n  - bridge_team_assign_assistance(scene: tensor) -> dict : Select an assisting robot.\n  - bridge_team_dispatch_assistance(robot: str) -> None : Dispatch the assisting robot.\n\nPrioritize team safety before attempting recovery.",
